<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Happy Birthday! ❤️</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff7675, #fbc2eb, #fdcb6e, #ff9a9e); 
            background-size: 400% 400%; animation: moveBG 12s ease infinite;
            min-height: 100vh; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; margin: 0; padding: 20px 10px; overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }
        @keyframes moveBG { 0%{background-position:0% 50%} 50%{background-position:100% 50%} 100%{background-position:0% 50%} }
        
        .card { 
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95); padding: 35px 25px; border-radius: 28px; 
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(255,118,117,0.3); text-align: center; max-width: 350px; width: 100%; 
            z-index: 10; position: relative;
        }
        .glass-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4) !important; backdrop-filter: blur(15px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); color: #4a4a4a;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255, 154, 158, 0.3) !important;
        }
        h1, h2 { color: #d63031; margin-top: 0; }
        input { 
            padding: 14px; border: 2px solid #ff9a9e; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; 
            margin-bottom: 20px; width: 90%; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); color: #333; outline: none;
        }
        .heart-btn { 
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b81, #ff4757); color: white; border: none; 
            padding: 14px 20px; border-radius: 50px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; 
            width: 90%; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 129, 0.4); transition: transform 0.1s ease;
        }
        .heart-btn:active { transform: scale(0.95); }
        .page { display: none; }
        .active-page { display: block; }
        .candle { font-size: 70px; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; animation: pulse 1.3s infinite; }
        @keyframes pulse { 0% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.1); } 100% { transform: scale(1); } }
        .wish-box { display: none; margin-top: 25px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold; color: #d63031; }
        .img-container { width: 230px; height: 230px; margin: 0 auto 15px auto; border-radius: 24px; border: 5px solid #ffccd5; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); overflow: hidden; }
        .gf-img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
        .wish-text { font-size: 17px; color: #2d3436; min-height: 70px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.6; padding: 0 10px; }
        .gift-particle { position: absolute; top: -50px; font-size: 26px; pointer-events: none; animation: fall linear infinite; z-index: 1; }
        @keyframes fall { 0% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); opacity: 1; } 100% { transform: translateY(110vh) rotate(360deg); opacity: 0; } }
        .phoo-text { position: absolute; color: #ff2a6d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; pointer-events: none; animation: flyUp 1s ease-out forwards; z-index: 100; text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px white; }
        @keyframes flyUp { 0% { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); opacity: 1; } 100% { transform: translateY(-80px) scale(1.3); opacity: 0; } }
        .music-box { margin-top: 18px; background: #fff0f3; padding: 10px; border-radius: 20px; border: 2px dashed #ff6b81; display: inline-block; width: 90%; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card glass-card page active-page" id="page1">
        <h2>🔒 Enter Password</h2>
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;">သဲငယ်ရဲ့မွေးနေ့Dateလေးနဲ့ဝင်ပေးပါ</p>
        <input type="password" id="passwordInput" placeholder="Password..."><br>
        <button class="heart-btn" onclick="verifyPassword(event)">အထဲဝင်မယ် 💖</button>
        <p id="errorMsg1" style="color:#ff4757; display:none; font-weight:bold; margin-top:15px;">Password မှားနေတယ်နော် ကလေး! 😜</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card glass-card page" id="page2">
        <h2>🎂 Make a Wish 🥰</h2>
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;">ကိတ်မုန့်လေးကိုနှိပ်ပေးပါကလေး</p>
        <div class="candle" id="candleIcon" onclick="cutCake()">🎂</div>
        <div class="wish-box" id="wishBox">
            <p>✨ "မွေးနေ့မှာ စိတ်ချမ်းသာ ကိုယ်ကျန်းမာနဲ့ လိုအင်ဆန္ဒတွေ အကုန်ပြည့်ပါစေ ကိုယ့်ရဲ့အမျိုးသမီးလေး" ✨</p><br>
            <button class="heart-btn" onclick="goToPage3(event)">နောက်တစ်ဆင့်သွားမယ် ❤️</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card glass-card page" id="page3">
        <h2>✨ နာမည်လေး ရိုက်ပေးပါဦး ✨</h2>
        <p style="color: #555; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;">ဖူးရဲ့ အင်္ဂလိပ်လို နာမည်လေးအပြည့်အစုံလေး ရိုက်ပါနော်</p><br>
        <input type="text" id="nameInput" placeholder="Enter Name..."><br>
        <button class="heart-btn" onclick="verifyName(event)">ဖွင့်ကြည့်မယ် 💖</button>
        <p id="errorMsg2" style="color:#ff4757; display:none; font-weight:bold; margin-top:15px;">နာမည်မှားနေပါတယ်! ပြန်ရိုက်ကြည့်ပါဦးနော် 😜</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card page" id="page4">
        <h1 id="finalTitle">Happy Birthday ပါ Phoo ❤️</h1>
        <div class="img-container">
            <img id="gfImage" src="image/gf1.jpg" class="gf-img">
        </div>
        <p id="finalWish" class="wish-text">🎂 ဒီနေ့ကျရောက်တဲ့ မွေးနေ့ကစပြီး စိတ်ချမ်းသာ ကိုယ်ကျန်းမာ ရှိပါစေ။</p>
        <button class="heart-btn" id="nextBtn" onclick="spawnPhoo(event); nextSlide()">နောက်တစ်ပုံ ကြည့်မယ် ➡️</button>
        
        <div class="music-box">
            <a href="https://youtube.com/playlist?list=RDuz7bvv9qQTU&playnext=1&si=PmBcasp5ohJfTFB9" target="_blank" style="color:#ff4757; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; font-size:14px;" onclick="spawnPhoo(event)">
                🎵 မွေးနေ့သီချင်း Playlist နားထောင်ရန် 💖
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        const items = ['🎁', '❤️', '🎈', '💖', '🎉', '🍰', '✨'];
        const imagePaths = ["image/gf1.jpg", "image/gf2.jpg", "image/gf3.jpg", "image/gf4.jpg", "image/gf5.jpg", "image/gf6.jpg"];
        const wishes = [
            "🎂 ဒီနေ့ကျရောက်တဲ့ မွေးနေ့ကစပြီး စိတ်ချမ်းသာ ကိုယ်ကျန်းမာ ရှိပါစေ။",
            "💖 အလိုချင်ဆုံး ဆန္ဒတွေလည်း အမြန်ဆုံး ပြည့်ဝပါစေ ကလေး‌လေး။",
            "🌟 ပညာရေး၊ စီးပွားရေးတွေလည်း ဒီထက်မက အောင်မြင်ပါစေ။",
            "🥰 ကိုယ့်အနားမှာ အမြဲတမ်း အကြာကြီး ရှိပေးပါဦးနော်။",
            "🎉 ကမ္ဘာပေါ်မှာ အပျော်ရွှင်ဆုံး အမျိုးသမီးလေး ဖြစ်ပါစေ။",
            "❤️ Happy Birthday ပါ မမဝေ ရေ...🤍"
        ];
        
        const loadedImages = [];
        imagePaths.forEach(src => {
            const img = new Image();
            img.src = src;
            loadedImages.push(img);
        });

        function createGifts() {
            for(let i=0; i<50; i++) {
                setTimeout(() => {
                    let p = document.createElement('div');
                    p.className = 'gift-particle';
                    p.innerText = items[Math.floor(Math.random() * items.length)];
                    p.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';
                    p.style.animationDuration = (Math.random() * 3 + 2.5) + 's'; 
                    document.body.appendChild(p);
                }, i * 200);
            }
        }
        window.onload = createGifts;

        function spawnPhoo(e) {
            for(let i=0; i<3; i++) {
                let txt = document.createElement('div');
                txt.className = 'phoo-text';
                txt.innerText = 'Phoo ❤️';
                txt.style.left = (e.clientX - 40 + (Math.random() * 60)) + 'px';
                txt.style.top = (e.clientY - 20) + 'px';
                document.body.appendChild(txt);
                setTimeout(() => txt.remove(), 1000);
            }
        }

        function verifyPassword(e) {
            spawnPhoo(e);
            let pass = document.getElementById('passwordInput').value;
            if(pass === "371998") {
                document.getElementById('page1').classList.remove('active-page');
                document.getElementById('page2').classList.add('active-page');
            } else {
                document.getElementById('errorMsg1').style.display = 'block';
            }
        }

        function cutCake() {
            document.getElementById('candleIcon').innerText = "🍰";
            document.getElementById('candleIcon').style.animation = "none";
            document.getElementById('wishBox').style.display = 'block';
        }

        function goToPage3(e) {
            spawnPhoo(e);
            document.getElementById('page2').classList.remove('active-page');
            document.getElementById('page3').classList.add('active-page');
        }

        function verifyName(e) {
            spawnPhoo(e);
            let name = document.getElementById('nameInput').value.trim().toLowerCase();
            if(name === "thetngonphoo") {
                document.getElementById('page3').classList.remove('active-page');
                document.getElementById('page4').classList.add('active-page');
            } else {
                document.getElementById('errorMsg2').style.display = 'block';
            }
        }

        let currentIndex = 0;
        function nextSlide() {
            currentIndex++;
            if (currentIndex >= imagePaths.length) currentIndex = 0;
            
            document.getElementById("gfImage").src = imagePaths[currentIndex];
            document.getElementById("finalWish").innerText = wishes[currentIndex];
            
            if (currentIndex === imagePaths.length - 1) { 
                document.getElementById("nextBtn").innerText = "ပြီးပါပြီ ❤️"; 
            } else { 
                document.getElementById("nextBtn").innerText = "နောက်တစ်ပုံ ကြည့်မယ် ➡️"; 
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
